HELP=$"
shared	none	 	files owned by more than one spell"

LONG=$"
Sometimes spells install the same files.
Usually, this is not a problem.
However, if becomes a problem those shared files
can be displayed using the shared command.

Sometimes piping shared into from provides more useful output.

# augur shared | augur from"

param(){ :;}

run(){
 find $INSTALL_INDEX -type f |
 xargs --max-lines=1024 cat |
 LC_ALL=C sort | uniq -d | files
}
